      <strong>Important:</strong> Add a persistent volume mounted at <code class="bg-amber-100 dark:bg-amber-900 px-1 py-0.5 rounded">/app/data</code> to keep your database across deployments.
    </p>
    <ul class="mt-2 text-sm text-amber-700 dark:text-amber-300 list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
