      <li><strong>Render:</strong> Disks → Add Disk → Mount path: <code>/app/data</code></li>
      <li><strong>Zeabur:</strong> Service → Storage → Path: <code>/app/data</code></li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <h2 id="setup-wizard">Complete the Setup Wizard</h2>

  <p>
    When you first open Jack, the Setup Wizard guides you through configuration:
  </p>

  <ol>
    <li>
      <strong>Property Info</strong> — Enter your property name and type (hotel, B&B, vacation rental)
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>AI Provider</strong> — Choose Local AI (free) or configure Claude/OpenAI
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Knowledge Base</strong> — Import information from your website or add manually
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Admin Account</strong> — Create your login credentials
    </li>
  </ol>

  <p>
    After setup, you'll be redirected to the login page. Use the credentials you just created.
  </p>

